title.narrative: Support to National Malaria Programme - Procurement of Services

description.narrative: This activity (Support to National Malaria Programme - Procurement of Services) is a component of Support to National Malaria Programme, Nigeria reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £58,118,259. This component benefits Nigeria, and works in the following sector(s): Health policy and administrative management, Medical research, Health education, Malaria control, Health personnel development, Business Policy and Administration. , with the following implementing partners: Baker Tilly Nigeria, Crown Agents Limited, Malaria Consortium, Oxford Policy Management. The start date is 01-08-2008 and the end date is 30-06-2016.
